el?\n\nFor a squirrel character like Herky, \"rustic\" usually means living in a way that feels natural, handcrafted, practical, and connected to the outdoors rather than polished, modern, or fancy.\n\nA rustic squirrel might have:\n\nA home made from hollow logs, tree stumps, or rough-hewn wood.\nHandmade furniture built from branches, bark, acorns, or reclaimed materials.\nSimple, durable clothing such as denim jackets, overalls, boots, or work shirts.\nTools hanging on the wall for gardening, repairing, or gathering food.\nQuilts, lanterns, baskets, and wooden shelves instead of sleek modern décor.\nA lifestyle that emphasizes hard work, self-reliance, and craftsmanship.\n\nLooking at the sketches you shared, Herky already feels quite rustic because:\n\nHe wears practical work clothes.\nHe owns tools like a rake, shovel, broom, and saw.\nHis home appears handmade and cozy rather than luxurious.\nThe environment suggests someone who builds, repairs, gardens, and spends time outdoors.\n\nIf you were describing Herky in a children\'s book, you might say:\n\nHerky was a rustic little squirrel who preferred a sturdy workbench to a fancy chair. His cozy woodland home was filled with tools, treasures, and the kind of things he had built with his own paws.\n\nOr:\n\nWith his worn denim jacket, sturdy climbing boots, and knack for fixing just about anything, Herky embodied the rustic spirit of the forest.\n\nFor a squirrel character, \"rustic\" often conveys warmth, reliability, and a connection to nature, almost like a woodland craftsman or small-town handyman.','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-02 21:31:56',NULL,NULL,NULL),(353,'dm_39_45',39,'OK. Right now I\'m working on another client. I\'ll do it after.','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-02 21:32:54',NULL,NULL,NULL),(354,'dm_39_45',45,'ok','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-02 21:33:07',NULL,NULL,NULL),(355,'dm_34_44',44,'400 total 3 illustration illustrations inn 2d and 3d \n200 ka link chahiya','te