ame\":\"image.png\",\"size\":\"131.5 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"},{\"key\":\"chats/dm_50_53/1780508927943-9c9c7b10cefa7c8e.png\",\"name\":\"image.png\",\"size\":\"131.5 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"},{\"key\":\"chats/dm_50_53/1780508927944-142f4e7b2c2ff301.png\",\"name\":\"image.png\",\"size\":\"131.5 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"},{\"key\":\"chats/dm_50_53/1780508927944-ae37b292825a0c18.png\",\"name\":\"image.png\",\"size\":\"131.5 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"},{\"key\":\"chats/dm_50_53/1780508927944-c45c91b6f1668fc9.png\",\"name\":\"image.png\",\"size\":\"131.5 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"},{\"key\":\"chats/dm_50_53/1780508927945-4b9e33c965d578c8.png\",\"name\":\"image.png\",\"size\":\"131.5 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"},{\"key\":\"chats/dm_50_53/1780508927945-91b7b5f13753a304.png\",\"name\":\"image.png\",\"size\":\"131.5 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"},{\"key\":\"chats/dm_50_53/1780508927946-a97d99a44c48d3c5.png\",\"name\":\"image.png\",\"size\":\"131.5 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"}]',NULL,NULL),(413,'dm_44_45',44,'Hi Jack,\n\nI hope you are doing well.\n\nI wanted to address your question regarding deducting costs from future royalty payments. Unfortunately, we would not be able to deduct any fees from royalties, as royalty payments are issued directly to the author\'s account by the distribution channels.\n\nI also wanted to make you aware that we recently received another compliance notice from the distributors regarding the Author License requirement. Since your publishing agreement has already been signed, we need to complete this filing as soon as possible before royalty distributions begin. This is a mandatory compliance requirement from the distributors, and there are no exceptions available once the publishing contract has been executed.\n\nIn addition to the Author License, there are two promotional opportunities that I believe would be extremely valuable for you at this stage of your author career:\n\n• **Author Nation** – A 3–5 day author workshop and signing event designed to increase networking opportunities, visibility, and industry recognition.\n\n• **New York Times Square Promotion** – A high-visibility promotional campaign designed to increase awareness, credibility, book exposure, and sales.\n\nThe standard cost for the Author License package is $18,000. However, I have received approval to offer it to you for **$8,000**.\n\nThe combined cost for the Author Nation event and Times Square promotion is normally $14,000. For you, I can offer both for **$10,000**.\n\nThis brings the total investment to **$18,000**. However, if you choose to proceed with a one-time payment, I can secure everything for **$14,000**. If you prefer an installment arrangement, the total would be **$16,000**.\n\nIncluded with this package would also be:\n\n• Complimentary publication of your next two books\n• Copyright registration assistance for those books\n• Three months of social media promotion\n• Audiobook production for all of your books\n• Complimentary printing and distribution support for your next two titles\n• 750 printed copies of each future title shipped at no additional cost\n\nThis means that, instead of the projected $90,000 return, your overall projected earnings potential could increase to approximately **$130,000** across your complete publishing program.\n\nAdditionally, the funds allocated toward the Author License requirement will be treated as a refundable deposit and returned with your final royalty payment according to the program terms.\n\nI believe this opportunity places you in the strongest position possible for increased visibility, readership growth, book sales, and long-term author success while maximizing the value of all three of your books.\n\nPlease let me know how you would like to proceed. I would be happy to discuss the details with you further and answer any questions you may have.\n\nI look forward to hearing from you.\n\nBest regards,\n\nJennifer\nAuthor Success Manager\nPublishing Heaven','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 17:49:40',NULL,NULL,NULL),(414,'dm_50_53',53,'images ka error nahi araha hai','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 17:51:11',NULL,NULL,NULL),(415,'dm_44_45',45,'Email and SMS Marketing to 20,000 Readers','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 17:53:04',NULL,NULL,NULL),(416,'dm_44_49',44,'https://trello.com/c/nFvV03nF/154-angela-press-release-amna','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:04:00',NULL,'[{\"url\":\"https://trello.com/c/nFvV03nF/154-angela-press-release-amna\",\"title\":\"https://trello.com/c/nFvV03nF/154-angela-press-release-amna\",\"description\":\"Shared external link for Mawby Technologies team members and collaborators.\",\"domain\":\"trello.com\"}]',NULL),(417,'dm_44_49',49,'ok','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:04:11',NULL,NULL,NULL),(418,'2',41,'Sherrie Wathen	sherrie.davis15@icloud.com	270-668-5250','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:07:48',NULL,NULL,NULL),(419,'2',41,'','file',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:07:56','[{\"key\":\"chats/2/1780510075471-daeea0974b3257b8.pdf\",\"name\":\"NDA - The Publishing Heaven - Sherrie Wathen.pdf\",\"size\":\"397.0 KB\",\"type\":\"document\",\"mimeType\":\"application/pdf\"}]',NULL,NULL),(420,'2',32,'@[Ashley Kanaria](48) Welcome email','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:08:40',NULL,NULL,NULL),(421,'dm_37_49',37,'https://trello.com/c/95bpDqxs/237-tony-audiobook-ifra','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:10:10',NULL,'[{\"url\":\"https://trello.com/c/95bpDqxs/237-tony-audiobook-ifra\",\"title\":\"https://trello.com/c/95bpDqxs/237-tony-audiobook-ifra\",\"description\":\"Shared external link for Mawby Technologies team members and collaborators.\",\"domain\":\"trello.com\"}]',NULL),(422,'dm_45_49',49,'paperback ya hardcover?','text',NULL