erfly visits, bedtime cuddles, playful adventures, and the meaning of kindness, patience, and unconditional love. But as the seasons change and the puppies begin to grow, something magical awakens beyond the garden fence... glowing lights, whispered secrets, and a mysteriouskeeper with a pointed red hat who may lead them toward Magical adventures unlike anything they\'ve ever imagined. A heartwarming story about family, friendship, courage, and the extraordinary magic hidden in ordinary moments. The Magical Adventures of the Sunshine Puppies is a gentle tale children will want to revisit again and again. Because sometimes the greatest adventures begin in the hearts and at home.','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:24:12',NULL,NULL,NULL),(449,'dm_50_53',53,'profile picture display nhi horhi khudki','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:35:36',NULL,NULL,NULL),(450,'dm_50_53',53,'active on off','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:36:01',NULL,NULL,NULL),(451,'5',30,'Hey','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:37:05',NULL,NULL,NULL),(452,'5',49,'yes','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:37:17',NULL,NULL,NULL),(453,'dm_33_49',33,'idhar aao','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:37:18',NULL,NULL,NULL),(454,'dm_33_49',33,'hogia purchase','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:37:20',NULL,NULL,NULL),(455,'dm_30_33',30,'ok','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:37:31',NULL,NULL,NULL),(456,'dm_50_53',53,'😀😂😊👍😍🙌🔥✨🚀💡✅❌👋🎉🙏💯','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 18:38:40',NULL,NULL,NULL),(457,'dm_50_53',53,'https://www.google.com/search?q=hourglass+hd&sca_esv=993fff11b0f34d9b&udm=2&sxsrf=ANbL-n5Oe_wuPVbuFEVZTDERHiQNECu-Mg%3A1780509281895&ei=YWogav-RNvz87_UPxL33kAw&biw=1600&bih=742&ved=0ahUKEwi_xpD60euUAxV8_rsIHcTeHcIQ4dUDCBE&uact=5&oq=hourglass+hd&gs_lp=Egtnd3Mtd2l6LWltZyIMaG91cmdsYXNzIGhkMgUQABiABDIEEAAYHjIEEAAYHjIEEAAYHjIGEAAYBRgeMgYQABgFGB4yBhAAGAUYHjIGEAAYBRgeMgYQABgFGB4yBhAAGAUYHkj_C1AdWMMGcAF4AJABAJgBtQ