em allows rights holders to submit professionally produced content for review. The basic process is:\n\nCreate a content provider account.\nSet up company, tax, and payment information.\nUpload the video files and required assets.\nAdd metadata (title, synopsis, cast, genre, language, artwork).\nSubmit the title for review.\nWait for Amazon\'s licensing decision. Reviews can take several weeks, and approval is not guaranteed.\n\nAmazon generally looks for professionally produced films and series rather than user-generated content.','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:01:59',NULL,NULL,NULL),(666,'dm_37_42',42,'','image',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:02:10','[{\"key\":\"chats/dm_37_42/1780527728125-7cca50d921835995.jpg\",\"name\":\"Bert-Book-Cover-4-(FF)-01.jpg\",\"size\":\"5.4 MB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/jpeg\"}]',NULL,NULL),(667,'dm_37_42',42,'nnh','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:02:12',NULL,NULL,NULL),(668,'dm_32_34',32,'Chat started on Friday, May 29, 2026 4:20:51 PM\n\n(4:20:51 PM) *** Gabriel Wu has joined the chat ***\n(4:20:51 PM) *** Visitor 18685236 has joined the chat ***\n(4:20:53 PM) Gabriel Wu: Hi there\n(4:20:58 PM) Gabriel Wu: How are you doing today?\n(4:21:02 PM) Gabriel Wu: Are you looking to get your manuscript published?\n(4:21:40 PM) Visitor 18685236: I need to publish a digital magazine and have 500 units printed for a marketing event\n(4:21:51 PM) Gabriel Wu: Sure!\n(4:22:03 PM) Gabriel Wu: I\'ll be glad to assist you with that :)\n(4:22:40 PM) Gabriel Wu: What is the Size of Magazine, Pages?\n\nand your Good name to address you?\n(4:23:09 PM) Visitor 18685236: the magazine will have 1 yearly issue. it is about 32 pages and it need professional editing, but very little as our team has fully reviewed it\n(4:23:26 PM) Gabriel Wu: Noted!\n(4:23:52 PM) Gabriel Wu: Is there a Deadline we should keep in mind for Publication and Printing?\n(4:24:02 PM) Visitor 18685236: June 15th\n(4:24:19 PM) Gabriel 