binson: Our team will share the Ebook version\n(4:30:43 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: I am looking for a cost effective solution no big expenses needed\n(4:30:54 PM) Matt Robinson: Sure\n(4:31:16 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: let me have a look at your ebook version to see what exactly you are talking about\n(4:31:31 PM) Matt Robinson: Its going to be a PDF version\n(4:31:35 PM) Matt Robinson: of your manuscript\n(4:31:54 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: PDF is something that anyone can do in Word\n(4:32:10 PM) Matt Robinson: Do you have any specifications for the Digital Version?\n(4:32:11 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: that is not what I have in mind\n(4:32:27 PM) Matt Robinson: Okay...\n(4:32:32 PM) Matt Robinson: So can you tell me a bit more?\n(4:32:38 PM) Matt Robinson: Like what do you have in your mind?\n(4:32:38 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: https://cioviews.com/magazines/\n(4:32:47 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: https://cioviews.com\n(4:33:02 PM) Matt Robinson: Alright\n(4:33:04 PM) Matt Robinson: Thats doable\n(4:33:57 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: I am thinking of something that people can open and flip pages back and forth as they wish\n(4:34:08 PM) Matt Robinson: Great idea!\n(4:34:17 PM) Matt Robinson: We can surely help you out with that as well.\n(4:34:27 PM) Matt Robinson: As soon as we get you onboard\n(4:34:54 PM) Matt Robinson: Your dedicated success manager will share some samples with you for the Flipbooks that we have created for our authors.\n(4:34:59 PM) Matt Robinson: Moreover, give me a moment\n(4:35:08 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: ok\n(4:35:15 PM) Matt Robinson: Let me share a quotation with you\n(4:35:26 PM) Matt Robinson: Kindly have a look and let me know if you have any questions\n(4:35:26 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: ok\n(4:36:20 PM) Matt Robinson: Included Services\nEditorial & Content Polish\n\n✓ Professional Editing & Proofreading\n✓ Editorial Cleanup & Refinement\n✓ Layout Consistency Review\n✓ Magazine Flow Optimization\n(4:36:27 PM) Matt Robinson: ✓ Premium Magazine Typesetting\n✓ Professional Layout Design\n✓ Interactive Digital Magazine Design\n✓ Clickable Online Flipbook Style Experience\n✓ Mobile & Desktop Optimized Viewing\n✓ Brand Consistency Setup For Future Annual Issues\n✓ High-Resolution Print Production Files\n(4:36:38 PM) Matt Robinson: Digital Magazine Delivery\n\nInstead of a basic PDF, our team will create:\n\n✓ A professional digital magazine browsing experience\n✓ Flipbook-style interactive viewing\n✓ Web-host-ready digital files\n✓ Embeddable online magazine setup\n✓ Shareable direct viewing link\n(4:36:59 PM) Matt Robinson: Printing & Physical Production\n\n✓ 500 Premium Printed Copies\n✓ US Letter Size\n✓ 32 Interior Pages\n✓ Premium Full Color Printing\n✓ 70# White Coated Paper\n✓ Paperback Perfect Bound\n✓ Glossy Cover Finish\n✓ Print Production Management\n✓ Delivery Coordination with Doorstep Delivery\n(4:37:50 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: yes, show me samples and please I am not rich, I am just fighting to get started on this business\n(4:37:57 PM) Matt Robinson: Magazine Specifications\nTrim Size: US Letter\nPage Count: 32 Pages\nBinding: Perfect Bound Paperback\nInterior Color: Premium Color\nPaper Type: 70# White Coated\nCover Finish: Glossy\n(4:38:23 PM) Matt Robinson: Annual Digital Magazine Production & Printing Package\nComplete Project Cost: $6,350\n(4:38:40 PM) Matt Robinson: Includes 500 Premium Printed Copies\n(4:39:03 PM) Matt Robinson: Timeline\n\nSince your target deadline is June 15th, this project would be treated as a priority production schedule.\n\nEstimated Timeline:\n\n10–14 Business Days\n\n(depending on approval turnaround)\n(4:39:19 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: Lets look at other options, that is over what I paid for my 215 book\n(4:39:40 PM) Matt Robinson: Is there a budget in your mind?\n(4:39:50 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: Let\'s just do editing and publishing\n(4:40:07 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: split the cost per service item to see what I can cover\n(4:40:11 PM) Matt Robinson: Sure thing\n(4:40:18 PM) Matt Robinson: Give me a moment please\n(4:40:22 PM) Matt Robinson: Kindly stay connected\n(4:41:55 PM) Matt Robinson: Essential Digital Magazine Package\nTotal Cost: $599\nIncluded Services\nEditorial & Refinement\n\n✓ Professional Editing & Proofreading\n✓ Editorial Cleanup\n✓ Layout Consistency Review\n✓ Final Content Polish\n\nDesign & Production\n\n✓ Professional Magazine Formatting\n✓ Premium Typesetting\n✓ Layout Adjustments\n✓ Print-Ready File Preparation\n✓ Digital Viewing Optimization\n\nInteractive Digital Magazine\n\n✓ Flipbook-Style Digital Magazine\n✓ Clickable Page-Turning Experience\n✓ Mobile & Desktop Compatible\n✓ Shareable Viewing Link\n✓ Web-Ready Files For Your Subdomain\n\nDeliverables Included\n\n✓ High-Resolution Print Files\n✓ Interactive Digital Magazine Version\n✓ Final Production Package\n✓ Future Annual Issue Structure Setup\n(4:42:24 PM) Matt Robinson: This includes publication as well!\n(4:43:03 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: Yes I can work with that\n(4:43:21 PM) Matt Robinson: Any questions for far?\n(4:43:41 PM) Matt Robinson: Also, as soon as we get you onboard I will assign you a Dedicated Success manager right away\n(4:44:02 PM) Matt Robinson: and just to clarify transparently, the main reason the earlier quotation was significantly higher was because of the 500-copy premium printing order\n(4:44:18 PM) Matt Robinson: Printing costs increase quite a bit when you factor in:\n\npremium full-color interiors\nglossy finish\ncoated paper stock\nperfect binding\n(4:44:39 PM) Matt Robinson: The digital magazine development, editing, formatting, and flipbook setup themselves are much more manageable cost-wise, which is why I restructured everything into the more practical $599 package focused on:\n\n✓ editing\n✓ formatting\n✓ professional layout\n✓ interactive flipbook experience\n✓ web-ready digital delivery\n✓ publication\n(4:45:22 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: Ok I agree\n(4:45:31 PM) Matt Robinson: That way, you can get the actual magazine professionally built and published first without overextending financially in the early phase of the project.\n(4:45:31 PM) Matt Robinson has changed the visitor\'s email address to cass@cassca.com.\n(4:46:14 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: Yes, I should be ready for payment by next wednesday, but I need an invoice to justify the payment\n(4:46:24 PM) Matt Robinson: https://zohoinvoicepay.com/invoice/thepublishingheaven/secure?CInvoiceID=2-45f0ac9b97c85085495b8ed7a9522350f850e6505617a24aad1f87900a6723beee232b6b423bdf8d76aebef32d41c11e8ad879d0e05856fae1b502e6cca49a8311e80a707f5b3196\n(4:46:32 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: invoice to CASSCA TECHNOLOGIES\n(4:46:35 PM) Matt Robinson: Your account has been created, Aderito!\n(4:46:43 PM) Matt Robinson: Give me a moment.\n(4:46:52 PM) Matt Robinson: Sharing another invoice with you.\n(4:47:53 PM) Matt Robinson: https://zohoinvoicepay.com/invoice/thepublishingheaven/secure?CInvoiceID=2-45f0ac9b97c85085495b8ed7a9522350c51c9c51c00f2379a1e9a5a41eb44dec4e376fe7f9a4880276aebef32d41c11e8ad879d0e05856fae1b502e6cca49a8311e80a707f5b3196\n(4:47:53 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: are you an online business or have an office in Phily ?\n(4:48:20 PM) Matt Robinson: We are based out of Newyork\n(4:48:29 PM) Matt Robinson: Also, kindly have a look at the invoice\n(4:48:41 PM) Matt Robinson: And let me know if anything needs to be changed\n(4:50:30 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: looks good\n(4:51:04 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: you dont pay taxes ?\n(4:51:32 PM) Aderito Cassolongo: I dont see it in the invoice. New York law does it enforce them invoices ?\n(4:51:51 PM) Matt Robinson: We dont charge our Customers\' taxes.\n(4:52:19 PM) Matt Robinson: Moreover, all the packages are exclusive of all taxes.\n(4:52:25 PM) Matt Robinson: Thats on us\n(4:52:52 PM) Matt Robinson: Also, I have shared everything with you over the email.\n(4:53:02 PM) Matt Robinson: Do check your spam, junk and inbox folders.\n(4:53:16 PM) Matt Robinson: Subject line: Digital Magazine Production Proposal\n(4: