mbers and collaborators.\",\"domain\":\"mixam.com\"}]',NULL),(678,'dm_32_49',49,'thankyou','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:19:11',NULL,NULL,NULL),(679,'dm_50_52',50,'[Forwarded]: ','image',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:22:05','[{\"key\":\"chats/dm_37_50/1780348816427-94dd6218c47797a4.png\",\"name\":\"Mawby Logo-01.png\",\"size\":\"74.2 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"}]',NULL,NULL),(680,'dm_50_52',50,'[Forwarded]: ','image',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:22:57','[{\"key\":\"chats/dm_50_52/1780520487758-3f6c36a7c77df524.png\",\"name\":\"image.png\",\"size\":\"16.4 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"}]',NULL,NULL),(681,'dm_50_52',50,'[Forwarded]: ','image',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:23:12','[{\"key\":\"chats/dm_50_52/1780520487758-3f6c36a7c77df524.png\",\"name\":\"image.png\",\"size\":\"16.4 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"}]',NULL,NULL),(682,'dm_50_52',50,'[Forwarded]: ','image',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:23:24','[{\"key\":\"chats/dm_37_50/1780348816427-94dd6218c47797a4.png\",\"name\":\"Mawby Logo-01.png\",\"size\":\"74.2 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"}]',NULL,NULL),(683,'dm_50_52',50,'[Forwarded]: ','image',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:23:45','[{\"key\":\"chats/dm_37_50/1780348816427-94dd6218c47797a4.png\",\"name\":\"Mawby Logo-01.png\",\"size\":\"74.2 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"}]',NULL,NULL),(684,'dm_34_46',46,'Apple TV\n\nApple generally does not allow most independent creators to upload movies directly. The usual route is through an approved distributor (aggregator).\n\nStep 1: Prepare Your Assets\n\nYou\'ll need:\n\nMaster video file (typically ProRes or high-quality MP4)\nTrailer\nPoster artwork\nThumbnail images\nSynopsis\nGenre\nCast and crew information\nClosed captions/subtitles (recommended)\nCopyright ownership documentation\nStep 2: Choose a Distributor\n\nCommon distributors include:\n\nFilmhub\nQuiver Digital\nBitmax\nStep 3: Submit Content\n\nUpload:\n\nVideo files\nArtwork\nMetadata\n\nThe distributor reviews technical specifications.\n\nStep 4: Apple Review\n\nThe distributor delivers the content to Apple.\n\nApple reviews:\n\nVideo quality\nAudio quality\nMetadata\nRights ownership\nStep 5: Go Live\n\nOnce approved, your animation becomes available on:\n\nApple TV\n\nRevenue comes from purchases and rentals according to your agreement.\n\nGoogle TV / Google Play Movies\n\nGoogle also generally works through distribution partners rather than accepting direct uploads from most creators.\n\nStep 1: Prepare Materials\n\nYou\'ll need:\n\nMaster video file\nTrailer\nArtwork\nSynopsis\nRatings information (if applicable)\nOwnership documentation\nStep 2: Use a Distributor\n\nPopular options:\n\nFilmhub\nBitmax\nQuiver Digital\nStep 3: Deliver Assets\n\nThe distributor converts and packages the content according to Google\'s specifications.\n\nStep 4: Review Process\n\nGoogle reviews:\n\nTechnical quality\nCopyright ownership\nMetadata accuracy\nStep 5: Publication\n\nOnce approved, your animation becomes available through:\n\nGoogle TV\n\nUsers can typically rent or purchase the content.\n\nRecommended Workflow for Independent Animators\n\nInstead of uploading separately everywhere, many creators use:\n\nOne distributor (such as Filmhub).\nUpload the animation once.\nSelect the platforms you want:\nAmazon Prime Video\nApple TV\nGoogle TV\nTubi\nThe Roku Channel\n\nThis is usually the simplest and most professional method because the distributor handles technical delivery, platform requirements, reporting, and royalty collection.','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:23:53',NULL,NULL,NULL),(685,'dm_50_52',50,'[Forwarded]: ','file',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:24:01','[{\"key\":\"chats/dm_37_50/1780528649376-052f409e63a20be4.pdf\",\"name\":\"The Living Thread Orchestra The Curved Mirror Return. (2).pdf\",\"size\":\"6.2 MB\",\"type\":\"document\",\"mimeType\":\"application/pdf\"}]',NULL,NULL),(686,'dm_37_50',50,'','video',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:24:20','[{\"key\":\"chats/dm_37_50/1780529059177-6096ecee92a0658f.mp4\",\"name\":\"600e0345497f49269fa496bb7e542da0-383dc40cb7509269.mp4\",\"size\":\"1.3 MB\",\"type\":\"video\",\"mimeType\":\"video/mp4\"}]',NULL,NULL),(687,'dm_44_49',49,'back ki pic sahi wali dedyn','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:24:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(688,'dm_44_49',49,'pixelate horhi','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:24:29',NULL,NULL,NULL),(689,'dm_50_52',50,'[Forwarded]: ','video',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:24:30','[{\"key\":\"chats/dm_37_50/1780529059177-6096ecee92a0658f.mp4\",\"name\":\"600e0345497f49269fa496bb7e542da0-383dc40cb7509269.mp4\",\"size\":\"1.3 MB\",\"type\":\"video\",\"mimeType\":\"video/mp4\"}]',NULL,NULL),(690,'dm_37_50',50,'[Forwarded]: ','video',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:25:32','[{\"key\":\"chats/dm_37_50/1780529059177-6096ecee92a0658f.mp4\",\"name\":\"600e0345497f49269fa496bb7e542da0-383dc40cb7509269.mp4\",\"size\":\"1.3 MB\",\"type\":\"video\",\"mimeType\":\"video/mp4\"}]',NULL,NULL),(691,'dm_35_49',35,'https://we.tl/t-KNw6NALtDbBY2n83','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:25:45',NULL,'[{\"url\":\"https://we.tl/t-KNw6NALtDbBY2n83\",\"title\":\"https://we.tl/t-KNw6NALtDbBY2n83\",\"description\":\"Shared external link for Mawby Technologies team members and collaborators.\",\"domain\":\"we.tl\"}]',NULL),(692,'dm_37_50',50,'[Forwarded]: ','image',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:25:58','[{\"key\":\"chats/dm_50_52/1780520487758-3f6c36a7c77df524.png\",\"name\":\"image.png\",\"size\":\"16.4 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"}]',NULL,NULL),(693,'dm_34_46',46,'Platforms That Allow Independent Publishing\nVideo & Audience-Building Platforms\nYouTube\nUpload directly.\nMonetize through ads, memberships, Super Thanks, etc.\nBest for animated series and children\'s content.\nVimeo On Demand\nUpload and sell/rent videos directly.\nSet your own pricing.\nFacebook Watch\nDirect video publishing.\nAudience-building rather than premium distribution.\nTikTok\nBest for shorts, clips, and promotion.\nInstagram\nReels and short-form animation.\nNewgrounds\nPopular among independent animators.\nPlatforms Where You Can Sell Directly\nVimeo On Demand\nUpload your animation.\nSet rental or purchase prices.\nKeep a share of the revenue.\nNo distributor required.\nYour Own Website\n\nUsing platforms like:\n\nWordPress\nShopify\n\nYou can:\n\nSell downloads.\nSell streaming access.\nOffer subscriptions.\n\nThis gives you the highest control and ownership.\n\nPlatforms That Usually Require a Distributor\n\nGenerally, you cannot independently upload professional movies or TV content directly to:\n\nApple TV\nGoogle TV\nNetflix\nDisney+\nHulu\nTubi\nThe Roku Channel\n\nThese platforms typically work with approved content partners, distributors, or direct licensing deals.\n\nWhat About Amazon Prime?\n\nHistorically, Amazon allowed many creators to upload through Prime Video Direct. However, Amazon has changed its policies over time and now focuses more on licensed and professional content. You should check the current requirements through Amazon Video Central before planning a direct-release strategy.','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:26:14',NULL,NULL,NULL),(694,'dm_34_40',34,'jo jo clients ki posts ready hain design ki tarafse un k cards ap project completed mein move krdein or posts laganay k bad marketing k board se bhi project completed mein krdiye ga','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:26:46',NULL,NULL,NULL),(695,'dm_34_40',34,'or last month ki reports nai aaein mere pas','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:26:56',NULL,NULL,NULL),(696,'dm_34_49',34,'https://trello.com/c/aaZrZMvI/371-tim-2d-animation-script-ifra','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-03 23:35:11',NULL,'[{\"url\":\"https://trello.com/c/aaZrZMvI/371-tim-2d-anima