",\"name\":\"ChatGPT Image Jun 4, 2026, 09_28_36 AM.png\",\"size\":\"2.1 MB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"}]',NULL,NULL),(766,'dm_34_44',44,'Hi Jack,\nI hope you are doing well.\nNo issues at all, and thank you for clarifying your position. I completely understand your decision regarding the appearances and events, and we can certainly set those aside and focus solely on the publication of your books.\nRegarding The Mystery of the Iniquity, the total cost for publication, copyrights, and all associated publishing requirements is $2,100.\nIn addition, to distribute the book to retail stores and make it available through our extended distribution network for 1,500 books, the cost would be $5,085.\nThis brings the total investment to $7,185, which includes everything needed to publish, protect, and distribute the book. Based on our projections, the estimated return for this book through store distribution is approximately $30,000.\nI also wanted to address one important point. I completely understand your concerns about costs, and I respect your decision regarding the promotional events. However, the Author License is not an optional promotional service, it is a required compliance filing. This license allows distributors to legally process and distribute royalty payments to you from around the world without delays or compliance issues.\nWithout the Author License on file, distributors may hold or delay royalty payments until the requirement has been satisfied. My concern is simply making sure that when your book begins generating sales, there are no obstacles preventing you from receiving your royalties promptly.\nBecause the Author License is one of the more expensive requirements, I spoke with my management team on your behalf. The standard cost is significantly higher, but after explaining your situation and your commitment to your publishing journey, I was able to secure special approval.\nOriginally, the total for the Author License was approved at $8,000, but we have been authorized to offer it to you for $5,000. This is the lowest amount the team is willing to approve, as it is a mandatory compliance requirement and the most important step in ensuring your royalties can be processed without interruption.\nWith the Author License included, the complete project total comes to $12,185.\nHowever, because you are one of my valued clients and I genuinely believe in your work, I have been able to secure an internal investment of $2,185 toward your project. This means the company will cover the publication and copyright costs, and you would only be responsible for the Author License and distribution portions.\nIn addition, we would like to include the following services at no additional cost. These services have a combined value of approximately $9,000:\n• Complimentary publication of your next two books\n• Copyright registration assistance for those books\n• Three months of social media promotion\n• Audiobook production for all of your books\n• Email and SMS marketing to 20,000 readers\n• Complimentary printing and distribution support for your next two titles\n• 750 printed copies of each future title shipped at no additional cost\nThese services are being provided entirely as a courtesy because I understand budget is a major consideration for you, and I want to help position your books for the greatest possible success.\nBased on our expanded projections, the estimated return potential increases from approximately $90,000 to $120,000 through the added distribution, marketing, and promotional support included in this package.\nI will also review the manuscript version you are resending to ensure we have the latest file and proceed accordingly.\nGod bless, and I look forward to hearing from you.\nWarm regards,\nJen','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-04 16:40:33',NULL,NULL,NULL),(767,'dm_34_44',44,'There are no hard edits remaining... please send a new contract ... no extras  to include the new book so I ca