erd when they were suddenly chased by a predator. Luckily, they managed to escape. However, their relief was short-lived; they soon encountered a massive anaconda. The snake tragically killed the Shepherd, forcing the terrified Rottweiler to run for her life.\n\nLater that day, a man found the wandering Rottweiler and tied her to a post by the side of the road. Fortunately, a kind-hearted lady, who was on her way to drop her children off at school, spotted the helpless dog. Deciding to rescue her, the lady brought the Rottweiler home and lovingly helped her set up a nursery.\n\nSoon after, the Rottweiler safely delivered her puppies. As the puppies grew, they lovingly took care of their mother. Later on, a policeman and another lady each asked to adopt one of the puppies. Tragically, a sudden disease struck the litter, and three of the puppies got sick and died. In the end, however, the Rottweiler and her four remaining puppies were saved and lived happily.','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-04 18:12:59',NULL,NULL,NULL),(806,'3',49,'@[Bilal Ghazi](39) Only work on Marshall\'s file need the complete book by tomorrow till 3 am','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-04 18:14:09',NULL,NULL,NULL),(807,'dm_32_41',32,'$750 now\nAnd $750 after publication','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-04 18:14:57',NULL,NULL,NULL),(808,'dm_32_41',32,'Elite Publishing Package','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-04 18:15:05',NULL,NULL,NULL),(809,'dm_32_41',32,'Kurt','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-04 18:15:12',NULL,NULL,NULL),(810,'dm_32_41',32,'full name lelena iska','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-04 18:15:16',NULL,NULL,NULL),(811,'dm_32_41',41,'Kurt Cherry\n4756787700716764\n05/27\n009\n\n32518 N Curtis Lane San an Arizona 85143','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-04 18:16:38',NULL,NULL,NULL),(812,'2',33,'@[Ibad Naseem](45) \nWelcome email','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-04 18:16:55',NULL,NULL,NULL),(813,'dm_34_44',44,'check','file',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-04 18:17:21','[{\"key\":\"chats/dm_34_44/1780597040154-d193598147c8ac19.docx\",\"name\":\"Distribution Contract - Jack Kelly.docx\",\"size\":\"267.2 KB\",\"type\":\"document\",\"mimeType\":\"application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document\"}]',NULL,NULL),(814,'2',32,'Recommended Package Option #2\nElite Author Brand, PR & Audiobook Campaign — $1,499\nThis is our most comprehensive author growth package, designed for authors who already have a published book and want to maximize visibility, establish a professional author brand, expand their audience, and launch their book across multiple formats—including audiobook distribution.\nSince your husband\'s book is already available on Amazon, our focus shifts from publication to discoverability, audience growth, brand building, and expanding into additional revenue channels.\nIncluded Everything From The $899 Author Growth & Marketing Package\nMarketing & Optimization\n✓ Amazon Listing Optimization\n✓ Advanced Keyword Research\n✓ Category Positioning\n✓ Metadata Optimization\n✓ Audience Demographic Setup\n✓ SEO-Based Book Positioning\n✓ Reader Targeting Strategy\nBranding & Visibility\n✓ Author Branding Consultation\n✓ Social Media Setup Guidance\n✓ 2 Months Social Media Marketing\n✓ Promotional Campaign Assistance\n✓ Author Profile Enhancement\nAdvanced Branding\n✓ Custom Author Website (3–5 Pages)\n✓ 1 Year Complimentary Domain & Hosting\n✓ Professional Author Branding Strategy\n✓ Brand Identity Consultation\n✓ Author Bio Enhancement\n✓ Professional Online Author Presence Setup\nExpanded PR & Media Exposure\n✓ Press Release Distribution Across 150+ Media Platforms\n✓ Expanded Media Visibility Campaign\n✓ Online Presence Enhancement\n✓ Brand Positioning Strategy\n✓ Public Relations Consultation\nAdvanced Marketing\n✓ Multi-Platform Promotional Campaigns\n✓ Advanced Amazon SEO Optimization\n✓ Reader Funnel Setup\n✓ Email Marketing Consultation\n✓ Community Growth Strat