*\n(1:42:38 PM) Matt Robinson: Hello\nHow\'re you doing today? :)\n(1:42:48 PM) Matt Robinson: Are you looking to get your manuscript published?\n(1:42:58 PM) Matt Robinson: This is a real human, not an Ai!\n(1:43:07 PM) Visitor 30490242: OK and yeah\n(1:43:13 PM) Matt Robinson: Sure\n(1:43:19 PM) Matt Robinson: May I know the genre of your book?\n(1:43:23 PM) Visitor 30490242 has changed their email address to rainydaysinthebambooforest@gmail.com.\n(1:43:23 PM) Visitor 30490242 has changed their name to Porter .\n(1:43:47 PM) Matt Robinson: Its a pleasure having you here with us, Porter!\n(1:43:56 PM) Matt Robinson: Can you tell me a bit about your book?\n(1:44:07 PM) *** Porter  has left ***\n(1:45:40 PM) Porter  is currently viewing https://www.theheavenpublishers.com/book-formating.html?matchtype=p&keyword=editing%20a%20book%20for%20publishing&{querystring}&gad_source=1&gad_campaignid=23856855799&gclid=CjwKCAjwxITRBhBYEiwA6mZm7W2UEnGHdwF1TSPa-B9sy4UN61AvvZRzC26rgaR7mBaewi45XQvAlBoC8QsQAvD_BwE.\n(1:45:46 PM) *** Matt Robinson has joined the chat ***\n(1:45:46 PM) *** Porter  has joined the chat ***\n(1:45:50 PM) Matt Robinson: Hey Porter!\n(1:45:52 PM) Matt Robinson: Welcome back\n(1:45:59 PM) Matt Robinson: Did you get my last message?\n(1:47:58 PM) *** Porter  has left ***\n(1:48:01 PM) Porter  is currently viewing https://www.theheavenpublishers.com/book-formating.html?matchtype=p&keyword=editing%20a%20book%20for%20publishing&{querystring}&gad_source=1&gad_campaignid=23856855799&gclid=CjwKCAjwxITRBhBYEiwA6mZm7W2UEnGHdwF1TSPa-B9sy4UN61AvvZRzC26rgaR7mBaewi45XQvAlBoC8QsQAvD_BwE.\n(1:48:05 PM) *** Matt Robinson has joined the chat ***\n(1:48:05 PM) *** Porter  has joined the chat ***\n(1:48:07 PM) Matt Robinson: Porter\n(1:48:10 PM) Matt Robinson: Would you like to connect over a quick call for better understanding & explanation?\n(1:48:22 PM) Porter : No I\'m just multitasking right now so the genere Young Adult Literary Fiction Dark Contemporary\n(1:48:31 PM) Matt Robinson: Sounds good\n(1:48:47 PM) Matt Robinson: Okay, so are you working on the manuscript right now or is it completed?\n(1:49:09 PM) Porter : I feel like it\'s done but it isn\'t that long\n(1:49:21 PM) Matt Robinson: How many pages do we have right now?\n(1:49:27 PM) Matt Robinson: An estimate would work as well\n(1:50:12 PM) Porter : Nine maybe but I labelled each page a chapter\n(1:50:21 PM) Matt Robinson: Awesome!\n(1:50:27 PM) Matt Robinson: and may I know like\n(1:50:34 PM) Matt Robinson: Are you looking to extend the story?\n(1:50:44 PM) Matt Robinson: Since we can help you out with Assistive Writing\n(1:50:49 PM) Matt Robinson: Or developmental editing\n(1:52:12 PM) Porter : I don\'t know because it feels finshed to me I just need another\'s opinion\n(1:52:21 PM) Matt Robinson: Got it!\n(1:52:24 PM) Matt Robinson: Also Porter\n(1:52:35 PM) Matt Robinson: Are you looking to get it published as an Ebook?\n(1:52:45 PM) Porter : ?\n(1:52:56 PM) Matt Robinson: We can publish your book\n(1:52:59 PM) Matt Robinson: as an Ebook\n(1:53:02 PM) Matt Robinson: Paperback\n(1:53:05 PM) Matt Robinson: And Hardcover\n(1:53:13 PM) Matt Robinson: So, do you have any personal preference?\n(1:53:52 PM) Porter : Can it start as an ebook and I do different one later on\n(1:54:03 PM) Matt Robinson: For sure!\n(1:54:07 PM) Matt Robinson: Also\n(1:54:15 PM) Matt Robinson: Will you be needing help with formatting\n(1:54:17 PM) Matt Robinson: Typesetting\n(1:54:22 PM) Matt Robinson: and Layout Adjustments?\n(1:54:37 PM) Porter : All the above yes\n(1:54:44 PM) Matt Robinson: Consider it done!\n(1:54:58 PM) Matt Robinson: Let me walk you through the process real quick\n(1:55:11 PM) Matt Robinson: Kindly have a look and let me know if you have any questions for me. :)\n(1:55:32 PM) Matt Robinson: The Process is really simple. \n\nOnce you have signed up, you will get a welcome email followed by a questionnaire that needs to be filled out and sent back to us with the manuscript.\