d Deal\n(2:00:46 PM) Matt Robinson: Including \nEditing\nTypesetting\nLayout Adjustments\n(2:00:50 PM) Matt Robinson: Book cover Designing\n(2:01:13 PM) Matt Robinson: ISBN + Barcode\nPublication on Amazon, Kindle, Kobo, Barnes & Noble\n(2:01:23 PM) Matt Robinson: With Unlimited Revisions for Everything\n(2:01:29 PM) Matt Robinson: for $199 Only!\n(2:01:56 PM) Matt Robinson: and and and\nThis is going to be a one time fee with no Hidden, monthly or yearly charges\n(2:02:17 PM) Porter : Military discount?\n(2:02:32 PM) Matt Robinson: I must say, Porter!\n(2:02:38 PM) Matt Robinson: Thank you for your service!\n(2:02:45 PM) Matt Robinson: Give me a moment please\n(2:02:53 PM) Matt Robinson: Let me check with our Finance team real quick\n(2:03:35 PM) Matt Robinson: After a 30% Veteran Discount \nAll you have to do is pay $139\n(2:03:46 PM) Matt Robinson: and our team will take care of everything for you\n(2:03:53 PM) Porter : Ok\n(2:04:03 PM) Matt Robinson: Are we ready to get started?\n(2:04:10 PM) Porter : Yes\n(2:04:15 PM) Matt Robinson: To create your account and get you onboard\n(2:04:19 PM) Matt Robinson: I will be needing your full name\n(2:04:25 PM) Matt Robinson: and your phone number please\n(2:04:59 PM) Porter : 9382339173 Braelyn Rain Porter\n(2:05:25 PM) Matt Robinson: Thank you!\n(2:05:29 PM) Matt Robinson: Here you go!\n(2:05:30 PM) Matt Robinson: https://zohosecurepay.com/billing/thepublishingheaven/secure?CInvoiceID=2-45f0ac9b97c850856f20a6b2eb9c0bdb23509bbfb149e72a7ba1d53487ec6f2e7366793fa45e8c8e76aebef32d41c11e8ad879d0e05856fa44e7d2aaa0c6ef0c11e80a707f5b3196\n(2:05:53 PM) Matt Robinson: Kindly click on the link and proceed with the order\njust let me know once done and I will assign you a Dedicated Success Manager right away\n(2:06:10 PM) Matt Robinson: Or if you want, I can ask my Billing team to give you a call and process the order for you.\n(2:06:15 PM) Matt Robinson: Let me know what suits you the ebst\n(2:06:18 PM) Matt Robinson: best*\n(2:07:4