inson has joined the chat ***\n(10:06:35 AM) *** Misty Grimes has joined the chat ***\n(10:06:37 AM) Matt Robinson: Hey\n(10:06:41 AM) Matt Robinson: Welcome back\n(10:06:43 AM) Misty Grimes: Hello\n(10:06:50 AM) Matt Robinson: I believe we got disconnected\nDid you get my last message?\n(10:06:56 AM) Misty Grimes: No\n(10:07:01 AM) Misty Grimes: I don’t think\n(10:07:02 AM) Misty Grimes: so\n(10:07:02 AM) Matt Robinson: how soon are you looking to get started?\n(10:07:16 AM) Matt Robinson: And is there a deadline we should keep in mind?\n(10:07:22 AM) Misty Grimes: Quickly.. I am shopping around at my options\n(10:07:28 AM) Matt Robinson: Alrighty\n(10:07:53 AM) Matt Robinson: Is there anything specific you\'re looking in a publisher?\n(10:08:08 AM) Matt Robinson: Feel free to let me know so I could share a best fit option\n(10:08:10 AM) Matt Robinson: Accordingly\n(10:08:41 AM) Misty Grimes: I’m not even sure where to start with that as this would be my first book\n(10:08:48 AM) Matt Robinson: Oh wow\n(10:08:55 AM) Matt Robinson: Congratulations on your first book, Misty!\n(10:09:02 AM) Matt Robinson: Let me walk you through the process real quick\n(10:09:12 AM) Misty Grimes: Thank you\n(10:09:16 AM) Misty Grimes: Ok\n(10:09:17 AM) Matt Robinson: The Process is really simple. \n\nOnce you have signed up, you will get a welcome email followed by a questionnaire that needs to be filled out and sent back to us with the manuscript.\n(10:09:29 AM) Misty Grimes: Ok 👍🏼\n(10:09:30 AM) Matt Robinson: ___________________________\nOnce we have that from your end, our design team would design the cover for you (if needed) and then will format the book to publication standards and then move forward with publication. \n\nEverything will be shared with you before making it live.\n(10:09:38 AM) Matt Robinson: At the time of publication, we will be putting in your banking details so whenever someone places an order, you will get the money directly into your account.\n(10:10:10 AM) Misty Grimes: Ok\n(10:10:20 AM) Matt Robinson: The best part is\n(10:10:25 AM) Matt Robinson: We offer Print on Demand\n(10:10:31 AM) Misty Grimes: Oh perfect\n(10:10:37 AM) Matt Robinson: So you wont be paying anything for the Printing and shipping of your books\n(10:10:43 AM) Matt Robinson: Amazon will be taking care of that for you\n(10:10:50 AM) Misty Grimes: Great\n(10:10:54 AM) Matt Robinson: We just charge a very minimal fees for the \nEditing\nTypesetting\n(10:10:58 AM) Matt Robinson: Layout adjustments\n(10:11:06 AM) Matt Robinson: Book Cover designing (If needed)\n(10:11:11 AM) Misty Grimes: Sure\n(10:11:18 AM) Matt Robinson: ISBN Assignment + Barcode\n(10:11:30 AM) Matt Robinson: Also Misty, since its your first book\n(10:11:35 AM) Matt Robinson: May I suggest you something?\n(10:11:40 AM) Misty Grimes: Sure\n(10:11:47 AM) Matt Robinson: Thank you!\n(10:11:52 AM) Matt Robinson: Since its almost done\n(10:12:07 AM) Matt Robinson: My suggestion would be to start with our Rapid Publishing Package\n(10:12:23 AM) Matt Robinson: Since it includes everything thats needed to get your book out there\n(10:12:39 AM) Matt Robinson: on all major platforms including\nAmazon\nkindle\nKobo\nGoogle Books\nBarnes & Noble\n(10:12:56 AM) Misty Grimes: Ok can I get pricing on your different packages?\n(10:13:01 AM) Matt Robinson: Our team will suggest you the Keywords as per the genre of your book\n(10:13:09 AM) Matt Robinson: Target audience\n(10:13:11 AM) Matt Robinson: and Genre\n(10:13:20 AM) Matt Robinson: Not only that, they will share all the do\'s and donts\n(10:13:29 AM) Matt Robinson: Just to give you a better understanding of everything\n(10:13:41 AM) Matt Robinson: Since its your intellectual property\n(10:13:52 AM) Matt Robinson: Nothing will go live without your approvals\n(10:13:55 AM) Misty Grimes: Ok perfect\n(10:14:07 AM) Matt Robinson: Also, you will be having 100% ownership rights as well as 100% Royalties\n(10:14:12 AM) Matt Robinson: Now, that being said\n(10:14:19 AM) Matt Robinson: That we share our Most Sold packages with you\n(10:14:30 AM) Matt Robinson: kindly have a look and let me know which package sounds good to you\n(10:15:37 AM) Matt Robinson: Rapid Publishing Package for $499\nAfter Discount $199 \n✓ Editing\n✓ Proofreading\n✓ Typesetting\n✓ Layout Adjustment\n✓ Formatting\n✓ Publication On 5 Major Platforms\n✓ EBook, Paperback & Hardcover Format\n✓ Custom 3D Book Cover Design(3-4 Mocks)\n✓ Unlimited Revisions\n✓ Dedicated Success Manager\n(10:16:18 AM) Matt Robinson: __________________________________________\nEnhanced Distribution & Visibility for $899\nAfter Discount $499\n✓ Editing\n✓ Formatting\n✓ Typesetting\n✓ Proofreading\n✓ Layout Adjustment\n✓ ISBN & Barcode\n✓ Publication On Amazon, Kindle, Barnes & Noble, Kobo, Lulu, Good Reads, Books a Million\n✓ Custom 3D Book Cover Design(3-4 Mocks)\n✓ Author Website (3-4 pages)\n✓ 1 year complementary domain and hosting\n✓ EBook, Paperback & Hardcover Format\n✓ Unlimited Revisions\n✓ Dedicated Success Manager\n(10:17:16 AM) Misty Grimes: Which five major platforms on the rapid package?\n(10:17:31 AM) Matt Robinson: Amazon\nKindle\nKobo\nGoogle Books\nBarnes & Noble\n(10:17:47 AM) Matt Robinson: You can cherry pick the platforms as well\n(10:18:01 AM) Misty Grimes: Ok awesome\n(10:18:09 AM) Misty Grimes: I like that package\n(10:18:17 AM) Matt Robinson: Great!\n(10:18:22 AM) Matt Robinson: That is our Most sold package\n(10:18:32 AM) Matt Robinson: Specifically designed for new Authors\n(10:18:45 AM) Matt Robinson: Moreover, you will be getting 5 Printed copies for free\n(10:18:51 AM) Matt Robinson: as a welcome gift from my end\n(10:18:57 AM) Matt Robinson: for your friends and family!\n(10:19:02 AM) Matt Robinson: Within this package\n(10:19:20 AM) Misty Grimes: Awesome\n(10:19:28 AM) Matt Robinson: Glad I could help!\n(10:19:35 AM) Matt Robinson: Misty kindly confirm your details\n(10:19:35 AM) Matt Robinson: Name: Misty Grimes\nEmail: misty.m.gromes1@gmail.com\nPhone: 8324342235\n(10:20:03 AM) Misty Grimes: my email should be Misty.m.grimes1@gmail.com\n(10:20:11 AM) Matt Robinson: Noted\n(10:20:14 AM) Matt Robinson: Give me moment \nLet me create your account real quick\n(10:20:17 AM) Matt Robinson: Kindly stay connected\n(10:20:27 AM) Misty Grimes: Ok\n(10:21:19 AM) Matt Robinson: Congratulations Misty!\n(10:21:26 AM) Matt Robinson: Your account has been created\n(10:21:31 AM) Matt Robinson: Here is the sign up link\n(10:21:31 AM) Matt Robinson: https://zohosecurepay.com/billing/thepublishingheaven/secure?CInvoiceID=2-45f0ac9b97c850856f20a6b2eb9c0bdb0618f009474786dd2bb7b4926c3e924377c16794b9da899276aebef32d41c11e8ad879d0e05856fa4570baaab4fe222511e80a707f5b3196\n(10:21:41 AM) Matt Robinson: Kindly click on the link and proceed with the order. Let me know once done\n(10:21:52 AM) Matt Robinson: So I can connect you with the Success Manager right away.\n(10:22:18 AM) Matt Robinson: Also, please note that you will be getting a Paid Invoice directly to your email as soon as you process the order.\n(10:23:51 AM) Misty Grimes: Done\n(10:24:01 AM) Matt Robinson: Welcome to the Publishing family, Misty!\n(10:24:10 AM) Matt Robinson: Kindly give me a moment\n(10:24:22 AM) Matt Robinson: Let me assign a Success Manager\n(10:26:15 AM) *** Misty Grimes has left ***\n(10:26:33 AM) Misty Grimes is currently viewing https://www.theheavenpublishers.com/book-publishing.html.\n(10:26:35 AM) *** Matt Robinson has joined the chat ***\n(10:26:35 AM) *** Misty Grimes has joined the chat ***\n(10:26:39 AM) Matt Robinson: Welcome to the Publishing family, Misty!\nKindly give me a moment\nLet me assign a Success Manager','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-05 17:26:58',NULL,'[{\"url\":\"https://www.theheavenpublishers.com/thankyou.html.\",\"title\":\"https://www.theheavenpublishers.com/thankyou.html.\",\"description\":\"Shared external link for Mawby Technologies team members and collaborators.\",\"domain\":\"theheavenpublishers.co