L,NULL,0,'2026-06-05 21:54:18',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1323,'4',42,'','image',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-05 21:56:25','[{\"key\":\"chats/4/1780696584639-41bcac1adbdc5087.png\",\"name\":\"image.png\",\"size\":\"17.5 KB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\"}]',NULL,NULL),(1324,'dm_32_48',32,'Beverly Ross\nachieve2day@gmail.com\n361-688-1380','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-05 22:40:32',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1325,'dm_32_48',32,'Chat started on Friday, June 05, 2026 3:23:18 PM\n\n(3:23:18 PM) *** Matt Robinson has joined the chat ***\n(3:23:18 PM) *** Visitor 76016330 has joined the chat ***\n(3:23:19 PM) Matt Robinson: Hello\n(3:23:22 PM) Matt Robinson: How are you doing?\n(3:23:27 PM) Matt Robinson: Are you looking to get your manuscript published?\n(3:24:55 PM) Matt Robinson: This is a real human, not an Ai!\n(3:25:14 PM) Visitor 76016330: I had my book published through another company and pulled it to republish it on Kindle through Amazon.  It is a 5x8 and they sent me my proofs which looked fine.  Then when I tried to publish it they will not except my cover.\n(3:25:44 PM) Matt Robinson: Got it\n(3:25:51 PM) Matt Robinson: May I know the genre of your book?\n(3:26:20 PM) Visitor 76016330: It is a Christian book called Choices and the Power to Achieve by Beverly Ross\n(3:26:41 PM) Matt Robinson: Its a pleasure having you here with us, Beverly!\n(3:26:52 PM) Visitor 76016330: Thank you\n(3:26:58 PM) Matt Robinson: Also, since we are a one stop solution we can surely help you out with the issue.\n(3:27:19 PM) Matt Robinson: Since the interior files have already been approved and your issue is specifically with the cover, this sounds more like a formatting or technical compliance problem rather than a content issue.\n(3:27:32 PM) Matt Robinson: The good news is that we can help with that.\n(3:27:34 PM) Visitor 76016330: Yes\n(3:28:02 PM) Matt Robinson: Our production team can review your existing cover file, identify exactly why Amazon KDP is rejecting it, and make the necessary adjustments to ensure it meets KDP\'s specifications, including:\n\n✓ Cover Size & Dimension Corrections\n✓ Spine Width Adjustments\n✓ Bleed & Margin Verification\n✓ Resolution & Image Quality Checks\n✓ Barcode Placement Review\n✓ KDP Compliance Formatting\n✓ Print-Ready Cover File Delivery\n✓ Publication of your book\n(3:28:35 PM) Visitor 76016330: ok\n(3:28:50 PM) Matt Robinson: In many cases, it\'s a relatively simple fix once we review the file requirements against Amazon\'s specifications.\n(3:29:18 PM) Visitor 76016330 has rated the chat Good\n(3:29:28 PM) Matt Robinson: do you currently have the original cover design files (PDF, PSD, AI, or source files) available?\n(3:29:41 PM) Visitor 76016330: Yes\n(3:30:07 PM) Matt Robinson: Perfect!\n(3:30:17 PM) Matt Robinson: In order to get a system generated quote for you\n(3:30:28 PM) Matt Robinson: May I have your email and phone number please?\n(3:30:41 PM) Visitor 76016330: achieve2day@gmail.com\n(3:30:57 PM) Visitor 76016330: 361-688-1380\n(3:31:00 PM) Matt Robinson: Thank you!\n(3:31:04 PM) Matt Robinson: Kindly stay connected\n(3:31:09 PM) Matt Robinson: Im sharing the cost now\n(3:32:03 PM) Matt Robinson: I see. Since the interior files have already been approved and the only issue preventing publication is the cover, we can take care of the entire process for you—from fixing the cover to getting the book published on Amazon KDP.\n\nSpecial Publication Assistance Package – $199\n\nIncluded Services\n\n✓ Complete Cover File Review\n✓ KDP Compliance Check\n✓ Cover Size & Dimension Corrections\n✓ Spine Width Adjustments\n✓ Bleed & Margin Fixes\n✓ Resolution & Print Quality Verification\n✓ Barcode Placement Review\n✓ Print-Ready Cover File Delivery\n\nPublication Support\n\nAmazon KDP Account Review\nPaperback Publication Setup\neBook Publication Setup (if applicable)\nMetadata Setup & Verification\nCategory Selection Assistance\nKeyword Optimization\nFinal File Upload Assistance\nPublication Submission & Approval Support\n\nAdditional Benefits\n\nDedicated Project Coordinator\nUnlimited Revisions on Cover Corrections\nDirect Assistance Throughout the Process\nNo Hidden Fees\n100% Ownership Rights Remain With You\n100% Royalties Remain With You\n\nTotal Project Cost: $199\n(3:32:53 PM) Visitor 76016330: I can\'t go there.  I will keep trying to figure it out.\n(3:33:02 PM) Matt Robinson: May I know like\n(3:33:07 PM) Matt Robinson: Whats holding you back?\n(3:33:14 PM) Matt Robinson: Anything I could help you with?\n(3:33:20 PM) Matt Robinson: If budget is a concern\n(3:33:22 PM) Matt Robinson: Do let me know\n(3:33:54 PM) Visitor 76016330: The fact that it is a simple fix that will take you less than 30 min. to fix.  I will see if I can figure it out.\n(3:34:14 PM) Matt Robinson: This includes Publication as well\n(3:34:29 PM) Matt Robinson: If you\'re looking to get the fixes for Cover\n(3:34:44 PM) Matt Robinson: it is just going to cost you $49\n(3:34:48 PM) Visitor 76016330: Amazon will be my publisher.  I have another book on there.\n(3:35:04 PM) Matt Robinson: Yes, Amazon will be the publisher\n(3:35:16 PM) Matt Robinson: We just charge a one time fee for the services mentioned above.\n(3:35:22 PM) Matt Robinson: If you\'re interested\n(3:35:34 PM) Matt Robinson: Do let me know and I will connect you with the Success Manager right away\n(3:36:54 PM) Visitor 76016330: connect me with them and we will see.\n(3:37:25 PM) Matt Robinson: Kindly confirm your details\n(3:37:44 PM) Matt Robinson: Beverly Ross\nachieve2day@gmail.com\n361-688-1380\n(3:38:14 PM) Visitor 76016330: I need my cover formatted so I can get kindle through Amazon to publish my book\n(3:39:10 PM) Matt Robinson: Got it\n(3:39:28 PM) Matt Robinson: May I know the best time to connect you with the Success Manager?\n(3:39:35 PM) Matt Robinson: Now, maybe?\n(3:39:41 PM) Visitor 76016330: yes','text',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2026-06-05 22:41:04',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1326,'dm_30_45',30,'De